Subject: [ghostium] window.devicePixelRatio hook

Spec-F wiring. Anchors at top of ``local_dom_window.cc``. The real
call into ``FingerprintNoiseSource::DevicePixelRatioOverride`` lands
inside ``LocalDOMWindow::devicePixelRatio()``. Like 0013, the hook
defers to any active ``Emulation.setDeviceMetricsOverride``.

---
 third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/local_dom_window.cc | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/local_dom_window.cc b/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/local_dom_window.cc
--- a/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/local_dom_window.cc
+++ b/third_party/blink/renderer/core/frame/local_dom_window.cc
@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@
